snippet.title: Best VGM 725 - Super Metroid - Brinstar ~ Red Soil
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 93 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2MzcVSPUJw0&fmt=18
Best VGM 396 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pTp4d38cPtc
Best VGM 1157 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CmMswzZkMYY
Best VGM 1447 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lz8ydvkFuo

Metroid Prime 2 version: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h3hLx-FVgKk

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Super Metroid (1994)
Brinstar ~ Red Soil
Kenji Yamamoto
